{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bc68f77201","title":"在重必武、林伯渠来电上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"22995297ad","index":0,"year":1944,"month":10,"day":19,"articleId":"bc68f77201"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d40d2b7ee","type":"paragraph","text":"在重必武、林伯渠来电上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"bc68f77201"},{"id":"9587bb0a63","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年10月19日）九月下半月至十月上旬，蒋对罗、丘压力，硬抗了几个星期在此期间，对我方亦表示硬性。但在双干演说出了一通气之后，文软下来。对美国软，对我方亦随着软些。部力子召集的国、共及中间三方会议，决定派五参政员来延及要求延安停止鸟蒋等，即其表现。蒋最怕指名批评他，美国亦怕我们不要将，故在许将存在条件下，可以作出一些有利于我们的交易来。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"bc68f77201"}],"page":{"id":"d0b136058f","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"bc68f77201","start":166,"end":166}}}},"__N_SSG":true}